"]},"Colorectal cancer":{"body":"# Colorectal cancer\n\nA common malignancy of the colon or rectum. This demo records two **negative** findings against it:\n[atorvastatin](../molecule/atorvastatin.md) `not_prevents` it, and [HMGCR (gene)](../gene/hmgcr.md)\nis `not_associated_with` it.\n","description":"Malignant neoplasm arising from the colon or rectum.","edges":[{"agent_type":"manual_agent","direction":null,"knowledge_level":"knowledge_assertion","negated":false,"note":null,"object":"Statins and colorectal-cancer risk (cohort)","predicate":"ReportedIn","primary_source":"Statins and colorectal-cancer risk (cohort)","publications":[],"qualifiers":{},"raw_predicate":"reported_in","reversed":false,"stats":{}}],"extra":{},"identifier":"Colorectal cancer","in_taxon":null,"node_type":"Disease","note":null,"path":"knowledge/disease/colorectal-cancer.md","raw_source":[],"raw_type":"Disease","subtype":"neoplasm","synonyms":["colorectal carcinoma","bowel cancer","CRC"],"tags":[],"timestamp":null,"xref":["MONDO:0005575","DOID:9256","MESH:D015179","ICD10:C18","UMLS:C0009402"]},"DrugBank":{"body":"# DrugBank\n\nAn **external-reference source node**: cited via the `infores:drugbank` CURIE in `xref`, with no\n`raw_source` (it is referenced, not ingested). It is the `primary_source` for the `binds` edge.\n","description":"Curated database of drugs and drug targets.","edges":[],"extra":{},"identifier":"DrugBank","in_taxon":null,"node_type":"Dataset","note":null,"path":"knowledge/dataset/drugbank.md","raw_source":[],"raw_type":"Dataset","subtype":"drug-database","synonyms":[],"tags":[],"timestamp":null,"xref":["infores:drugbank"]},"HMGCR (gene)":{"body":"# HMGCR (gene)\n\nEncodes HMG-CoA reductase, the enzyme [atorvastatin](../molecule/atorvastatin.md) inhibits. A\nMendelian-randomization analysis in the cohort found **no association** between HMGCR variation and\n[colorectal cancer](../disease/colorectal-cancer.md) — the symmetric `not_associated_with` edge.\n","description":"Protein-coding gene encoding HMG-CoA reductase, the rate-limiting enzyme of cholesterol synthesis and the statin target.","edges":[{"agent_type":"data_analysis_pipeline","direction":null,"knowledge_level":"statistical_association","negated":true,"note":null,"object":"Colorectal cancer","predicate":"NotAssociatedWith","primary_source":"Statins and colorectal-cancer risk (cohort)","publications":[],"qualifiers":{},"raw_predicate":"not_associated_with","reversed":false,"stats":{"p_value":0.41}},{"agent_type":"manual_agent","direction":null,"knowledge_level":"knowledge_assertion","negated":false,"note":null,"object":"Statins and colorectal-cancer risk (cohort)","predicate":"ReportedIn","primary_source":"Statins and colorectal-cancer risk (cohort)","publications":[],"qualifiers":{},"raw_predicate":"reported_in","reversed":false,"stats":{}}],"extra":{},"identifier":"HMGCR (gene)","in_taxon":"NCBITaxon:9606","node_type":"Gene","note":null,"path":"knowledge/gene/hmgcr.md","raw_source":[],"raw_type":"Gene","subtype":"protein_coding","synonyms":["HMG-CoA reductase gene","LDLCQ3"],"tags":[],"timestamp":null,"xref":["HGNC:5006","NCBIGene:3156","ENSEMBL:ENSG00000113161","OMIM:142910"]},"Statin antitumor activity (preprint)":{"body":"# Statin antitumor activity (preprint)\n\nAn ingested **preprint** source node that was **retracted**. Its `meta.yaml` records\n`credibility.retracted: true` and `tier: preprint`, so any claim citing it (the `treats` edge on\n[atorvastatin](../molecule/atorvastatin.md)) should be flagged as weak/untrustworthy evidence.\n","description":"Retracted preprint claiming high-dose atorvastatin shrinks colorectal tumors.","edges":[{"agent_type":"manual_agent","direction":null,"knowledge_level":"prediction","negated":false,"note":null,"object":"Colorectal cancer","predicate":"UsedToStudy","primary_source":"Statin antitumor activity (preprint)","publications":[],"qualifiers":{},"raw_predicate":"used_to_study","reversed":false,"stats":{}}],"extra":{},"identifier":"